  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your air fryer to 375°F.",
    "Sift the flour into a mixing bowl. Mix in the coconut milk, egg yolks, heavy cream, butter, baking powder, vanilla extract, and salt until smooth.",
    "Pour the mixture into an oven-safe dish or flan ring (paleo-friendly alternative can be used).",
    "Bake for 40 minutes at 350°F. Let it cool slightly before serving.",
    "Serve with a drizzle of air-fried tomato sauce and garnished with paleo-friendly crumbled feta cheese or tofu."
